rwhelmed by a toxic amount of a substance, leading to severe physiological distress and, in many cases, death. It's crucial to understand that addiction is a complex health condition, not a moral failing, and overdose deaths are preventable with the right interventions.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-115_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-116_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-117_ pf-heading-1-h3">Key facts and statistics</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_4479c3e5-312a-4608-a35d-cabc6d2d52c6.jpg?v=1710763593" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/mohdizzuanbinroslan_4479c3e5-312a-4608-a35d-cabc6d2d52c6.jpg?v=1710763593 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Naloxone Training Resources: Empowering Communities on IOAD - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Naloxone Training Resources: Empowering Communities on IOAD - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-119_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-120_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by mohdizzuanbinroslan via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-122_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-123_ pf-text-1">According to the World Health Organisation, approximately 585,000 people die each year globally due to drug use, with overdose being a leading cause of death among people who use drugs.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-125_ pf-text-1">In the United States alone, over 93,000 people died from drug overdoses in 2020, representing a staggering increase compared to previous years.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-127_ pf-text-1">Opioids, including prescription painkillers and heroin, are among the most common substances involved in overdose deaths.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-129_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-130_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-131_ pf-heading-1-h3">How International Overdose Awareness Day engages learners</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ending_Stigma_Overdose_Awareness_Events_and_Advocacy_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710776387" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Ending_Stigma_Overdose_Awareness_Events_and_Advocacy_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710776387 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Ending Stigma Overdose Awareness Events and Advocacy - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Ending Stigma Overdose Awareness Events and Advocacy - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-133_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-134_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by orcearo via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-136_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-137_ pf-text-1"><b>Education and awareness campaigns</b> - Organisations worldwide use International Overdose Awareness Day to launch educational campaigns aimed at informing the public about overdose prevention strategies, recognising the signs of overdose, and promoting harm reduction practices.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-139_ pf-text-1"><b>Community events and memorials</b> - Vigils, memorial services, and community gatherings provide learners with opportunities to honour those lost to overdose, share personal stories, and raise awareness about the human impact of the overdose crisis.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-141_ pf-text-1"><b>Training and skill-building workshops</b> - Learners can participate in training sessions on overdose prevention and response, including learning how to administer naloxone. This life-saving medication can reverse opioid overdoses.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-143_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-144_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-145_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Addiction_Support_Services_A_Resource_for_Overdose_Prevention_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710777094" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Addiction_Support_Services_A_Resource_for_Overdose_Prevention_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710777094 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Addiction Support Services: A Resource for Overdose Prevention - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Addiction Support Services: A Resource for Overdose Prevention - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-147_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-148_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by yavdat via Envato Elements</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eGPXGI hfOvrX pf-150_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-151_ pf-text-1"><b>Get informed</b> - Educate yourself and others about overdose prevention strategies and the signs of overdose.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-153_ pf-text-1"><b>Support harm reduction initiatives</b> - Advocate for policies that prioritise harm reduction, treatment access, and support services for individuals struggling with substance use disorders.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-hAcGzb caRPsV pf-155_ pf-text-1"><b>Get involved</b> - Participate in International Overdose Awareness Day events and support organisations working to address the overdose crisis.</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-157_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-158_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-159_ pf-heading-1-h3">Conclusion</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Taking_Action_Against_the_Opioid_Crisis_International_Overdose_Day_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710777254" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Taking_Action_Against_the_Opioid_Crisis_International_Overdose_Day_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710777254 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Taking Action Against the Opioid Crisis International Overdose Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Taking Action Against the Opioid Crisis International Overdose Day - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-161_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-162_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by LightFieldStudios via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-164_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">International Overdose Awareness Day serves as a crucial reminder of the human toll of addiction and overdose. By engaging learners through education, advocacy, and support, we can work together to prevent overdose deaths and build healthier, more compassionate communities.</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-jrQzAO jIEVBe pf-166_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-gIDmLj bESFPC pf-167_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-hmjpVf IvCUC pf-168_ pf-heading-1-h3">Saving lives together - Navigating the path to prevention on International Overdose Awareness Day</h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Overdose_Prevention_Programs_Join_the_Fight_Against_Addiction_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710777409" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Overdose_Prevention_Programs_Join_the_Fight_Against_Addiction_-_Rose_Mabiza_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1710777409 1536w" width="1000" height="667" alt="Overdose Prevention Programs Join the Fight Against Addiction - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " title="Overdose Prevention Programs Join the Fight Against Addiction - Rose Mabiza - The Mandatory Training Group UK - " data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-jQrDum jseZXh pf-170_ pf-image-1"/><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-171_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Image by foto_pstryki via Envato Elements</p><p class="sc-eLwHnm fPjVqe pf-173_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">Explore our collection of resources and solutions for International Overdose Awareness Day, including educational materials, training programs, and support networks, to join the global effort to prevent overdose deaths and support those affected by addiction.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-